name: CHORAO EDUCATIONAL SOCIETY
briefDescription: CHORAO ED. SOCIETY FOUNDED IN 1970 IS MANAGING A NURSERY & KG SCHOOL(1996),ENGLISH PRIMARY SCHOOL(1996),MARATHI PRIMARY SCHOOL(2012),HIGH SCHOOL-ENG. MEDIUM(1970),HIGHER SEC. SCHOOL(ARTS & COMMERCE)-1994 IN CHORAO ISLAND VILLAGE OF N. GOA DISTRICT IN THE STATE OF GOA.556 STUDENTS ARE STUDYING IN OUR SCHOOLS IN 13-14,90% OF WHICH BELONG OBC,ST & SC LOW INCOME COMMUNITIES.
